comments: Harrell (LAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Walker's (BOS) path.
Theis (BOS) absorbs the contact initiated by Williams' (LAC) during his driving shot attempt.
Leonard (LAC) and Tatum (BOS) engage and disengage off-ball.
Tatum (BOS) extends his off arm slightly during the drive as he passes Leonard (LAC). The contact is marginal and does not affect Leonard's ability to defend.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Leonard's (LAC) path.
Leonard (LAC) does not put part of his hand under the ball and bring it to a pause.
Morris Sr. (LAC) briefly grasps and releases Hayward's (BOS) jersey.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Shamet's (LAC) path and does not deliver any contact.
Harrell (LAC) and Leonard (LAC) both make clean contact with the ball during Theis' (BOS) play at the basket.
Smart (BOS) makes "high-five" contact with Leonard (LAC) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Theis (BOS) and Morris Sr. (LAC) engage during the rebound.
Hayward (BOS) makes marginal contact with Morris Sr. (LAC) after he has released the ball and returned to the floor.
Williams (LAC) makes clean contact with the ball.
Replay review of the foul called on Leonard (LAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Leonard (LAC) makes contact to Walker's (BOS) face with his elbow at the end of the drive.

Following the foul call on Leonard (LAC), BOS called a timeout and then LAC requested a valid Coachs Challenge. Since the challenge was unsuccessful, LAC was charged the timeout and not BOS. BOS then was required to call another timeout in order to be able to advance the ball.
Walker (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Leonard's (LAC) path and does not deliver any contact.
Coffey (LAC) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
There are no angles available that can confirm conclusively whether or not Coffey (LAC) makes contact with Walkers (BOS) arm during the shot attempt.
Shamet (LAC) briefly places an arm around Smart (BOS) as the pick concludes.
Smart (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Shamet's (LAC) path and does not deliver any contact.
Harrell (LAC) makes clean contact with the ball and does not deliver contact to Williams (BOS) as they engage and disengage during the rebound.
Tatum (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball at the start of Leonard's (LAC) drive and maintains a legal guarding position during the drive.
Leonard (LAC) extends his leg on the driving shot attempt but does not affect with Tatum's (BOS) ability to defend.
Tatum (BOS) makes "high-five" contact with Leonard (LAC) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Shamet (LAC) makes contact with Smart's (BOS) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Williams (BOS) legally contest Williams' (LAC) jump shot attempt.
At the end of the drive at 00:53, Shamet (LAC) establishes himself in a legal defensive position and absorbs the contact initiated by Tatum (BOS) during his drive.

At the end of the drive at 00:53, Tatum (BOS) gathers the ball on his left foot while progressing and steps with his right foot to establish a pivot foot. He then turns on his pivot foot, steps and then jumps from his left to shoot, releasing the ball before returning his pivot foot to the floor.
Tatum (BOS) places a hand on Leonard's (LAC) back at the end of the drive, but does not affect his SQBR.
Tatum (BOS) makes "high-five" contact with Leonard (LAC) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) extends his arms away from his body at the end of the pick and makes marginal contact with Shamet's (LAC).
Leonard (LAC) places a hand on Tatum's (BOS) side on the gather and immediately removes it without delivering any contact during Tatum's driving shot attempt.

Hayward (BOS) commits a take foul by making contact with Williams' (LAC) arm before his upward shooting motion, which is required for him to be in the act of shooting on a jump shot. The shot is immediately waved off and the ball correctly given to LAC on the sideline.
Leonard (LAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Walker's (BOS) path.
Tatum (BOS) legally contest Shamet's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Shamet (LAC) brushes Tatum's (BOS) leg after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Williams (BOS) slightly extends a forearm to Harrell's (LAC) back as Harrell's momentum is taking him forward to receive the pass.
Shamet (LAC) makes marginal contact with Tatum (BOS) during his drive.
After Williams (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball, he makes incidental contact with Harrell (LAC). The reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Tatum (BOS) does not extend his arm and push off or drive through Shamets (LAC) space, who is in a legal guarding position.
Hayward (BOS) cleanly blocks Williams' (LAC) driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Shamet's (LAC) path.
Harrell (LAC) makes marginal contact with Williams' (BOS) as he releases to rebound.
Williams (LAC) makes contact with Tatum's (BOS) arm at the end of the drive.
Williams (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Harrell's (LAC) path and briefly grasps and releases Harrell's arm during the pick.
Harrell (LAC) makes contact with Hayward's (BOS) arm that affects his ability to pass.
Hayward (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball during the inbound pass.
Williams (LAC) makes contact with Hayward's (BOS) arm.
Williams (BOS) legally contest Mann's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Wanamaker (BOS) makes contact with Motley's (LAC) arm during his play at the basket.
